nodes.text: A female Yuuzhan Vong tried to sneak a concealed villip into one of the Prophet Yu'Shaa's heresy preachings. However, she was caught by Kunra, and Nom Anor, the Yuuzhan Vong behind the mask of Yu'Shaa, ordered the warrior to extract the information of whom the villip's partner belonged to before killing the female Yuuzhan Vong.
